name: Hell Broke Luce
description:
What did you do before the war? I was a chef, I was a chef. What was your name? It was Geoff, Geoff. I lost my buddy and I wept, wept. I come down from the meth so I slept, slept. I had a good home but I left, left. Pantsed at the wind for a joke, I pranced right in with the dope. Now I'm home and I'm blind and I'm broke. What is next...

Oil, canvas, madness.
